{"tid":1683692,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你地班連登仔究竟打完飛機未 你地輸鳩哂架啦 成日話警察驚清算 驚移唔到民 佢地班低學歷生物有撚擔心過咩","createTime":"2019-10-30T17:44:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T11:24:29.000Z","uid":252492,"like":66,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"ff26c9d32f3a4f3d943a80d7513be691c8b7fb95","tid":1683692,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T17:44:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/207097505984138/posts/3313123815381476?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F207097505984138%2Fposts%2F3313123815381476%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=VY3E9QkOBFFWjsPhNJvPHudFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=c3ebd581\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/207097505984138/posts/3313123815381476?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n一條片答撚左你 班撚樣由頭到尾都未驚過<br />\n清算？你班撚樣剩識係側邊鳩叫黑社會 唱肥媽既垃圾 佢地驚你老母閪臭？<br />\n<br />\n前線就出面打生打死 每次比人拉成百人<br />\n前線已經買小見小 另一邊人就好似4年前金鐘大台唱k豬咁事不關己係到摺連豬抽水拿光環<br />\n<br />\n根本已經步入佔中末期輸鳩哂啦<br />\n等到前線繼續比人拉 你班仆街冷氣軍師繼續唔出黎或摺連豬<br />\n到前線無撚哂人 政棍出黎食人血饅頭話戰場轉去選舉<br />\n成個運動下場就變4年前佔中翻版<br />\n<br />\n你班仆街連登仔打夠飛機著返條褲未？"},{"pid":"67ca1ce79518478acb549852e04ef91294de0cb5","tid":1683692,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T17:46:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"250a522ee0e30b1bec9b7ba9e811ff57a1b807cb","tid":1683692,"uid":200495,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T17:47:56.000Z","msg":"佢哋仲幻想緊報應論 幻想緊清洗黑警架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"358d6028a34ef80cf91bf56ce2ca7fa8b4229541","tid":1683692,"uid":239842,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T17:47:58.000Z","msg":"輸又點贏又點？<br />\n連登仔控制到咩？<br />\n<br />\n出面淨係吹風叫全民勇武，人唔笑狗都吠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5f100c159555d0b2be6e9f231909179656d79c2","tid":1683692,"uid":235025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T17:48:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9a00704c42c1ef6d082338b8cc815885215e9ec6","tid":1683692,"uid":252492,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"250a522ee0e30b1bec9b7ba9e811ff57a1b807cb","tid":1683692,"uid":200495,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T17:47:56.000Z","msg":"佢哋仲幻想緊報應論 幻想緊清洗黑警架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T17:50:44.000Z","msg":"成日話黑警會驚清算 驚移唔到民<br />\n班低學歷英文都唔識多個既生物 搬大灣區都黎唔切啦 <br />\n<br />\n成班連登仔剩識打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5e19e40d651c0f8db13f0e24bee1c70df92ba01","tid":1683692,"uid":167428,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T17:51:55.000Z","msg":"留係香港做土皇帝幾好，洗撚去外國"},{"pid":"7311430e527ed0ff7a8546616d065b68fe69b276","tid":1683692,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T17:56:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f423e735b433f5abe0b5f1c4ebf4336ff2327942","tid":1683692,"uid":51349,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T17:58:57.000Z","msg":"係咁絕望 政府唔驚 大9晒既話<br />\n777唔撚洗日日出黎 叫人割啦<br />\n根本經濟攬炒 力量係好大<br />\n你覺得係打飛機咁咪慢慢睇<br />\n如果一路堅持冇效,政府唔驚既話<br />\n唔會有南華早報 政府中人 放風 話換人/成立獨立調查委員會啦<br />\n<br />\n慢慢放負啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a6a52fa1db87b63f00bff630c32998036326b6f","tid":1683692,"uid":80851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T17:59:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b579ae0b9e84f5edf491b7ac39efe2f7e0fabab","tid":1683692,"uid":60563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T18:03:42.000Z","msg":"條片既留言同樓主風向完全唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然我認同樓主所講<br />\n不過其實又唔洗咁負<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一日未殺到埋身佢地唔會知道黨都一定會清算佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82c4d52652fc72752a3f8979e19ee622bf7decd0","tid":1683692,"uid":289751,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T18:03:57.000Z","msg":"佢地擔唔擔心關我L事<br />\n事實係呢場運動係點佢地都會做condom<br />\n777會做condom, 佢地都會<br />\n呢個係中共處理手法, 唔係輸贏問題"},{"pid":"6f5a5e6c29afca41873b26a5d6d658444a2ce512","tid":1683692,"uid":153811,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T18:05:53.000Z","msg":"腦子進水麻。<br />\n<br />\n講多幾句呢d 半獸話可以刺激兒登仔死去活來。<br />\n做大事一d 智慧都冇，下下幻想某個體制，部隊會被清算。幻想中共清楚警察呢種呢種幼稚思想，你信清算會發生，姐係承認更高層既中共，呢種隱性主奴意識形態仲係度，學人諗住打到一個體制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9832756944d2c4dc6b8ada47b3c9453c4454a2a7","tid":1683692,"uid":262043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82c4d52652fc72752a3f8979e19ee622bf7decd0","tid":1683692,"uid":289751,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T18:03:57.000Z","msg":"佢地擔唔擔心關我L事<br />\n事實係呢場運動係點佢地都會做condom<br />\n777會做condom, 佢地都會<br />\n呢個係中共處理手法, 唔係輸贏問題"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T18:06:14.000Z","msg":"冇腦又易控制既兵點解會變condom"},{"pid":"6ff4062311a2708715897889bab5c1050c6c9635","tid":1683692,"uid":80851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T18:07:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f63b8a80d95a10e8e5fb8c4ae4657d2b1b3fb57f","tid":1683692,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T18:12:44.000Z","msg":"有兩個點<br />\n1.清唔清算同抗爭成唔成功無咩關係 已經係後事<br />\n2.點會咁易清算 係咪ON9<br />\n<br />\n講得出乜撚野移唔移到民既主張極致天真同低能"},{"pid":"6367d5bc43aa85c6c16cc1164324f0c2b82cc300","tid":1683692,"uid":165136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T18:20:43.000Z","msg":"其實分兩邊睇，低級同高級影響唔同<br />\n<br />\n識啲低級警務人員嘅都知佢哋大部份生活都唔大<br />\n通常喺香港，返大陸<br />\n最多去下日本台灣，東南亞咁<br />\n人權法案美國制裁對佢哋影響唔大<br />\n如果話將來想移民會有影響，的確係<br />\n但你要明白低級啲友諗嘢諗唔到咁遠，三，五年頂盡<br />\n你話埋比佢知都唔會理你，個腦去唔到咁遠處<br />\n<br />\n當然有限制好過完全無後果<br />\n高級啲嗰班本身都係貪福利，之後就走人架啦<br />\n諗住移民嘅係會大影響<br />\n<br />\n不過遲下其他國家有類似制裁<br />\n擴展到歐洲亞洲區，日本嗰啲<br />\n對高低級都有影響嘅<br />\n話就話可以返大陸，實際真係個個想住大灣區咩<br />\n講就好呀好呀，住一個星期就頂唔順啦"},{"pid":"3519cf8247f1eab6ec087f88b4459aea37ad985b","tid":1683692,"uid":6347,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T18:22:28.000Z","msg":"係呀，輸撚晒<br />\n我好能驚呀"},{"pid":"4fcc3586f179a0c4a228a2ef91a4f81f1746fb7d","tid":1683692,"uid":270563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T18:24:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"545474568df9c45a36c1ff440e6334ffa95f6d00","tid":1683692,"uid":289751,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"9832756944d2c4dc6b8ada47b3c9453c4454a2a7","tid":1683692,"uid":262043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82c4d52652fc72752a3f8979e19ee622bf7decd0","tid":1683692,"uid":289751,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T18:03:57.000Z","msg":"佢地擔唔擔心關我L事<br />\n事實係呢場運動係點佢地都會做condom<br />\n777會做condom, 佢地都會<br />\n呢個係中共處理手法, 唔係輸贏問題"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T18:06:14.000Z","msg":"冇腦又易控制既兵點解會變condom"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T18:52:36.000Z","msg":"中共要香港繼續幫佢地生金蛋就要平熄民憤<br />\n就算呢場運動抗爭者係輸左比人拉哂<br />\n民怨都唔會就咁消失<br />\n香港作為金融中心唔可以一直處於戒嚴狀態<br />\n中共為左表現出佢地係可以&quot;持平&quot;同埋令香港人屈服<br />\n就會清算班官同popo黎熄民憤<br />\n呢個係中共一直以來既手法, 64就係最好既例子<br />\n班popo唔覺得會被清算係因為佢地對中共了解太少<br />\n令外中共唔信香港人, 包括popo<br />\n唔會比popo拎黑材料去美國篤灰換綠卡既機會<br />\n要講聽話易控制加心狠手辣, 有咩係popo做到武警做唔到?"},{"pid":"b90d63fcc61c70963d581f56190b778e9705e2a3","tid":1683692,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T01:07:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c329c690ea0decd52e26fb511bb46d8425982a41","tid":1683692,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T02:56:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"910fa41e9567e9889e067ec83011e57de420bcf2","tid":1683692,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:07:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88328d344a4bc59717e72eb8d80338c5c9912eab","tid":1683692,"uid":28159,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f423e735b433f5abe0b5f1c4ebf4336ff2327942","tid":1683692,"uid":51349,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T17:58:57.000Z","msg":"係咁絕望 政府唔驚 大9晒既話<br />\n777唔撚洗日日出黎 叫人割啦<br />\n根本經濟攬炒 力量係好大<br />\n你覺得係打飛機咁咪慢慢睇<br />\n如果一路堅持冇效,政府唔驚既話<br />\n唔會有南華早報 政府中人 放風 話換人/成立獨立調查委員會啦<br />\n<br />\n慢慢放負啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:13:36.000Z","msg":"689 14年嗰陣有冇成日提要回復正常，要同暴力切割？<br />\n柒婆成日提住呢兩樣嘢<br />\n今次堅係提哂水話你知和勇不分，經濟攬炒就搞到佢好頭痕"},{"pid":"45b3d61fe9307a52018b67d9bfd13d7ed22b3b31","tid":1683692,"uid":320676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:15:59.000Z","msg":"所以就要進化，打撚死佢哋，唔係佢哋唔識驚。<br />\n和理非都要進化，一見到狗就圍起佢哋屌，再運武器畀最前排嘅人，打撚死啲狗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不分和勇，大家都係革命義士<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1683656\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1683656</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cce9b51185808c86d0699cc4bdb19831e9cc21ec","tid":1683692,"uid":810,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:17:37.000Z","msg":"依場運動根本唔會有終點<br />\n咪on9啦<br />\n政府民望同警隊信任度會因為你所謂輸撚左而反彈?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有依家中小學生都出黎運動<br />\n佢地大個左會突然痴返去政府個邊?<br />\non99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4fd8f76fabd23e86aef74bc55dea0de09e78ebf","tid":1683692,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:30:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2954eace1d036fffb7737f743ae6a7dc90e8395d","tid":1683692,"uid":19218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:30:51.000Z","msg":"散仔根本未驚過，佢地預左係香港生活到老，仲要有政府<br />\n<br />\n撐"},{"pid":"c67426f57be04c95260d3e481f8c479cb1b894f1","tid":1683692,"uid":35347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:31:54.000Z","msg":"點解你會覺得唔離開香港就制裁唔到佢哋？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20efd863922822ad39cc88453743f4f8e2b01fcb","tid":1683692,"uid":48667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f423e735b433f5abe0b5f1c4ebf4336ff2327942","tid":1683692,"uid":51349,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T17:58:57.000Z","msg":"係咁絕望 政府唔驚 大9晒既話<br />\n777唔撚洗日日出黎 叫人割啦<br />\n根本經濟攬炒 力量係好大<br />\n你覺得係打飛機咁咪慢慢睇<br />\n如果一路堅持冇效,政府唔驚既話<br />\n唔會有南華早報 政府中人 放風 話換人/成立獨立調查委員會啦<br />\n<br />\n慢慢放負啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:51:04.000Z","msg":"但係要做到經濟攬炒,<br />\n最有效都係要日頭就逼到啲鋪頭關門先得, <br />\n而唔係等到夜晚先黎關門"},{"pid":"a886e5899b8283300c88259d520cae6d209ef512","tid":1683692,"uid":309873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f423e735b433f5abe0b5f1c4ebf4336ff2327942","tid":1683692,"uid":51349,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T17:58:57.000Z","msg":"係咁絕望 政府唔驚 大9晒既話<br />\n777唔撚洗日日出黎 叫人割啦<br />\n根本經濟攬炒 力量係好大<br />\n你覺得係打飛機咁咪慢慢睇<br />\n如果一路堅持冇效,政府唔驚既話<br />\n唔會有南華早報 政府中人 放風 話換人/成立獨立調查委員會啦<br />\n<br />\n慢慢放負啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T04:00:44.000Z","msg":"真係只能敢做咩就做咩！<br />\n你話我自私同無膽我認，我只敢湊人頭式遊行、捐錢同杯葛。<br />\n<br />\n下下屌鳩啲人自私，只會越黎越少人，我就唔會畀你屌到上面啲野都唔做既，但有無人係咁我就唔擔保啦。<br />\n<br />\n連登近月好多人吹風同屌和理非，我起左樓主底相信係真心既唔係風向撚，但真係唔好做埋啲同風向卧底一樣既野啦！"},{"pid":"3df34737889180048045dc73f25af1f06c55821f","tid":1683692,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T05:30:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdac7b92de5ce76a43a566659d6d1d83c9f8fd62","tid":1683692,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T05:37:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37265315dd3a3eba2d9fe21f1c363290b0728090","tid":1683692,"uid":197540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T05:38:52.000Z","msg":"本身個目標係政權, 警察只係 side quest<br />\n放負夠未? 拉"},{"pid":"84e18f4306185c62cb5abfbf79df459ed83c9175","tid":1683692,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T07:04:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b508043e3f23276d03a6fac6e7057ed83e3d49f6","tid":1683692,"uid":14520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff26c9d32f3a4f3d943a80d7513be691c8b7fb95","tid":1683692,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T17:44:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/207097505984138/posts/3313123815381476?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F207097505984138%2Fposts%2F3313123815381476%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=VY3E9QkOBFFWjsPhNJvPHudFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=c3ebd581\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/207097505984138/posts/3313123815381476?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n一條片答撚左你 班撚樣由頭到尾都未驚過<br />\n清算？你班撚樣剩識係側邊鳩叫黑社會 唱肥媽既垃圾 佢地驚你老母閪臭？<br />\n<br />\n前線就出面打生打死 每次比人拉成百人<br />\n前線已經買小見小 另一邊人就好似4年前金鐘大台唱k豬咁事不關己係到摺連豬抽水拿光環<br />\n<br />\n根本已經步入佔中末期輸鳩哂啦<br />\n等到前線繼續比人拉 你班仆街冷氣軍師繼續唔出黎或摺連豬<br />\n到前線無撚哂人 政棍出黎食人血饅頭話戰場轉去選舉<br />\n成個運動下場就變4年前佔中翻版<br />\n<br />\n你班仆街連登仔打夠飛機著返條褲未？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T07:53:41.000Z","msg":"對啲次次有發夢嘅人黎講<br />\n佢地仲要做啲咩？"},{"pid":"7b98151e3cb7d78d6d3f89b694e614ad678c4822","tid":1683692,"uid":160650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T07:56